snippet.title: Total War: PHARAOH - Dynasties Overview
snippet.description:
Ruin the world, or save it. It's all in your hands. 👐
Dynasties, the huge FREE update to Total War: PHARAOH, arrives 25th July.
📜 Check out the updated FAQ here: https://community.totalwar.com/pharaoh-faq

TOTAL WAR: PHARAOH AVAILABLE NOW - https://store.totalwar.com/en/total-war/total-war-pharaoh

Official Total War Store: https://store.totalwar.com/en/total-war/total-war-pharaoh
Steam: https://store.steampowered.com/app/1937780/Total_War_PHARAOH/
Any questions? Check out the FAQ: https://totalwar.com/blog/total-war-pharaoh-faq
